1.To print the one is adult based his/her age 
Note: Don't print if not adult 

pseudo:routine 
function IsAdult(age)
isAdult = (age >= 18);
return isAdult;

pseudo:routine test
function TestIsAdult(): -> None
Input age 
if(IsAdult(age)) 
  print 'You are an adult.'
end if



2.Take a num 10, if num greater than 5 ,print "num as 'greater than 5'"

pseudo:routine 
function IsGreaterThan5(num)
IsGreaterThan5 = (num > 5);
return IsGreaterThan5;

pseudo:routine test
function TestIsGreaterThan5()
Input num 
if(IsGreaterThan5(num)) 
  print 'Number is greater than Five.'
end if




3.To print 'number is positive' if num > 0,it should not print if not positive 

pseudo:routine 
function IsPositiveNum(num)
IsPositiveNum= (num > 0);
return IsPositiveNum;

pseudo:routine test
function TestIsPositiveNum()
Input num 
if(IsPositiveNum(num))
  print 'Number is positive.'
end if




4.if temp > 25, print it is hot outside.

pseudo:routine 
function CheckTemp(temp)
CheckTemp= (temp > 25);
return CheckTemp;

pseudo:routine test
function TestCheckTemp()
Input temp
if(CheckTemp(temp))
  print 'It is hot outside.'
end if





5. To print the is adult or not based his/her age. 

pseudo:routine 
function IsAdult(age)
isAdult = (age >= 18);
return isAdult;

pseudo:routine test
function TestIsAdult()
Input age 
if(IsAdult(age)) 
  print 'You are an adult.'
else 
  print 'You are not an adult.'
end if




6.Input mark, if IsMarkGreaterThan40(mark) print pass else fail  

pseudo:routine 
function IsMarkGreaterThan40(mark)
IsMarkGreaterThan40 = (mark >= 40);
return IsMarkGreaterThan40;

pseudo:routine test
function TestIsMarkGreaterThan40()
Input mark 
if(IsMarkGreaterThan40(mark)) 
  print 'pass.'
else 
  print 'fail.'
end if





7. To check the person adult, teenager or child 
    for given age 
    function IsAdult(age) -> boolean 
        isAdult = (age >= 18);
        return isAdult; 
    function IsTeenager(age) -> boolean 
        isTeenager = (age >= 13);
        return isTeenager; 
    function TestIsAdultTeenagerOrChild(): -> None
        Input age 
        if(IsAdult(age)) 
            print 'You are an adult.'
        else if(IsTeenager(age)) 
            print 'You are a teenager.'
        else
            print 'You are a child.'
        end if


